title: 613. Vikings vs. Bears Scouting Report + Brian Kelly on Notre Dame's Undefeated Season
itunes:title: 613. Vikings vs. Bears Scouting Report + Brian Kelly on Notre Dame's Undefeated Season
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode. To start off, the guys give their takeaways from the MNF game between the Vikings and Bears, while looking back at Vikings WR Justin Jefferson's scouting report and comparing his skill set to some of the top receivers in the league (:30). Then, Notre Dame head football coach Brian Kelly joins as he discusses building Notre Dame, the challenges of playing through the pandemic, developing his players, playing in the ACC this season and emphasizes the importance of relating to his players (11:52). To wrap up the show, the pair react to the main points from the interview (34:05).
